## Scope Limitation

This repository is intentionally limited to standards documentation and lightweight CI/CD automation. It does not contain, and is not intended to contain, large-scale code surfaces such as servers, runtime libraries, or workflow engines. Such implementations should live in dedicated downstream repositories.

